    "longBusinessSummary": "Cat Lai Port Joint Stock Company provides shipping agency services in Vietnam. The company also offers sea transport agency, maritime brokerage, shipping towage, cargo loading and unloading at seaports, and trading international multimodal transport services, as well as shipping brokerage, ship supply, cargo counting, and ship repair and cleaning services. It also provides business international multimodal transport services; building and repair of containers and trailers; customs brokerage and logistics services; and transportation of goods by car, inland waterway, and oversized and overweight vehicles. In addition, the company involved in loading and unloading equipment; buying, selling, and leasing ships, containers, and transporting equipment for super long and heavy goods; and constructing civil, industrial, and irrigation works. Cat Lai Port Joint Stock Company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
